<p><a name="Overview" id="Overview"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nuclear_fusion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Overview">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Overview</span></h2>
